/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係真係好有陰影<br />\n唔理我老母依家幾錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都原諒唔到佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"我明，無論點已經從內心討厭呢個人，點可以做得出手<br />\n利申 老豆依加都係仆街，唔撚錫"},{"pid":"2c13d53627de9af34f123af47f60b1ebd179b83f","tid":1023182,"uid":177004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:58:27.000Z","msg":"同時間同四個女人有婚外情"},{"pid":"147756e89f25f96c4822ddd91c07305d53a2f2d9","tid":1023182,"uid":120722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"吸毒，打屋企人，借財仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇個天幾時收佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c273ea4813a57887415d4fc28d6d6307e7c4e68a","tid":1023182,"uid":85311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">家暴</span><br />\n<br />\n係我面前打鳩老母 當時太細唔識反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到而家大左都仲歷歷在目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7110b0039ba26df59ae43f7f8113d0f8254c40","tid":1023182,"uid":152982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"無問過我生我出黎仲要我跟佢地思維方式長大<br />\n然後由我細細個開始就逼9我番教會<br />\n格9硬要我做耶撚dllm<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb981f800a20599b98c7cf9e29081a037025ac7","tid":1023182,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:19:04.000Z","msg":"兩歲時唯一一段記憶：<br />\n因為唔識嗌其中一位全名而喪打。<br />\n<br />\n8-9歲發生：<br />\n攞住把刀亂揮，雖然唔係對住我；<br />\n因為自己覺得屋企人做錯野而連埋我一齊趕出門口；<br />\n唔同意佢等於駁嘴，打到喊再打到收聲為止；<br />\n掉咗我視為生命一樣重要嘅寵物，第一次仲識自己搵路番黎，過兩日後再掉走，從此冇再見過佢；<br />\n<br />\n中間大大小小仆街野太零碎。<br />\n<br />\n20歲：<br />\n對另一位太過份，我出聲制止，結果燒埋我嗰啖想郁手。我捉住佢隻手，佢想扭開，我再加大力，佢唔要命咁係咁扭。最後比佢逼到頂唔順發脾氣打穿道門，成隻手冇哂感覺，佢仲要拗落去要贏，要維持佢係屋企嘅地位。嗰刻我就知道我對佢唔需要再有感情。之後？關節deformity，雖然唔太影響日常，但對佢黎講：who fucking cares?佢只有同我講我捉住佢隻手大力到佢第二日番工用唔到力。<br />\n<br />\n對另一位最憎嘅記憶：<br />\n直至今日都係廢人一般從來冇為我出半句聲。"},{"pid":"93717f2d08222d957617b4e8f97d4d13c17b50de","tid":1023182,"uid":9962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"話我係垃圾，令佢地好失望；<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359ee1311fb301756b2414aea6f2491873f0d595","tid":1023182,"uid":92065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"因為工作性質關係成日會接觸到小朋友<br />\n同佢地相處得多真係覺得<br />\n「屌你班老豆老母唔識教/唔教/唔理個仔說就唔好生佢出黎害9佢啦」"},{"pid":"b8ed4d2c1e3aa098e89dc66e2d117b92a2aa4ae1","tid":1023182,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:56:01.000Z","msg":"搞咗個呀妹出嚟"},{"pid":"c15b7dd659d7d432ac16dc8b9c0312f1060e1224","tid":1023182,"uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}